mp;width=481\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Calibri, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Cam Ranh Riviera Beach Resort &amp; Spa</strong></em>&nbsp;sở hữu tổng cộng 70 ph&ograve;ng cao cấp, được bố tr&iacute; trong 8 khu nh&agrave; nghỉ dưỡng v&agrave; 14 biệt thự c&oacute; hồ bơi ri&ecirc;ng. Mỗi ph&ograve;ng đều được thiết kế v&agrave; trang tr&iacute; độc đ&aacute;o với sự kết hợp h&agrave;i h&ograve;a giữa phong c&aacute;ch kiến tr&uacute;c đương đại c&ugrave;ng nội thất phương T&acirc;y hiện đại đảm bảo du kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;i l&ograve;ng từ c&aacute;i nh&igrave;n đầu ti&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Calibri, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"huong-tron-3n2d-trang-mat-ngot-ngao-tai-cam-ranh-riviera-beach-resort-spa-chi-2tr888-ivivu-3\" class=\"wp-image-229751 aligncenter\" height=\"473\" src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2017/10/huong-tron-3n2d-trang-mat-ngot-ngao-tai-cam-ranh-riviera-beach-resort-spa-chi-2tr888-ivivu-3.png\" style=\"margin: 0.4em auto 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block;\" width=\"810\" /></p>\r\n<div class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" id=\"attachment_229752\" style=\"margin: 0.4em auto 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Calibri, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; max-width: 96%; text-align: center; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); width: 1090px;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Ảnh: @olga_mokrushina777\" class=\"Ảnh: @olga_mokrushina777 wp-image-229752 size-full\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2017/10/huong-tron-3n2d-trang-mat-ngot-ngao-tai-cam-ranh-riviera-beach-resort-spa-chi-2tr888-ivivu-4.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 98%; height: auto; display: block;\" title=\"Ảnh: @olga_mokrushina777\" width=\"1080\" />\r\n	<p class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.92857rem; line-height: 1.39286rem; font-family: &quot;Roboto Slab&quot;, Palatino, Cambria, &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">\r\n		Ảnh: @olga_mokrushina777</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Calibri, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Kh&ocirc;ng gian ấm c&uacute;ng, ri&ecirc;ng tư của những căn ph&ograve;ng như một chất &ldquo;x&uacute;c t&aacute;c&rdquo; gi&uacute;p cho đ&ocirc;i bạn trẻ tăng th&ecirc;m hương vị ngọt ng&agrave;o v&agrave; thăng hoa c&ugrave;ng nhau. Th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o đ&oacute;, chỉ v&agrave;i ph&uacute;t bước ra khỏi ph&ograve;ng nghỉ, cả hai đ&atilde; c&oacute; thể nắm tay nhau dạo trong khu&ocirc;n vi&ecirc;n xanh mướt, thả m&igrave;nh đung đưa tr&ecirc;n những chiếc v&ograve;ng của khu resort hay tr&ecirc;n B&atilde;i D&agrave;i &ndash; một b&atilde;i biển quyến rũ của Nha Trang.</p>\r\n<div class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" id=\"attachment_229753\" style=\"margin: 0.4em auto 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Calibri, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; max-width: 96%; text-align: center; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); width: 858px;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Ảnh: @katysik_istomina\" class=\"Ảnh: @katysik_istomina wp-image-229753\" height=\"843\" src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2017/10/huong-tron-3n2d-trang-mat-ngot-ngao-tai-cam-ranh-riviera-beach-resort-spa-chi-2tr888-ivivu-5.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 98%; height: auto; display: block;\" title=\"Ảnh: @katysik_istomina\" width=\"848\" />\r\n	<p class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.92857rem; line-height: 1.39286rem; font-family: &quot;Roboto Slab&quot;, Palatino, Cambria, &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">\r\n		Ảnh: @katysik_istomina</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" id=\"attachment_229754\" style=\"margin: 0.4em auto 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Calibri, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; max-width: 96%; text-align: center; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); width: 1090px;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Ảnh: @marine_kazaryan\" class=\"Ảnh: @marine_kazaryan wp-image-229754 size-full\" height=\"718\" src=\"https://cdn3.ivivu.com/2017/10/huong-tron-3n2d-trang-mat-ngot-ngao-tai-cam-ranh-riviera-beach-resort-spa-chi-2tr888-ivivu-6.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 98%; height: auto; display: block;\" title=\"Ảnh: @marine_kazaryan\" width=\"1080\" />\r\n	<p class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.92857rem; line-height: 1.39286rem; font-family: &quot;Roboto Slab&quot;, Palatino, Cambria, &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"